<div id=title>
  <span class="h1 f-bold text-green-600">
    Help
  </span>
</div>
<%
  short_keys = {
    'Space': 'Play / Pause',
    '← / →': 'Seek back / forward',
    'z / x': 'Set ayah start / end',
    'a / d': 'Previous / next ayah',
    's / f / n': 'Slower / faster / normal speed',
    'Ctrl/Cmd + Z': 'Undo',
    'Ctrl/Cmd + Shift + Z': 'Redo'
  }
%>
<div id=body>
  <style>
      kbd {
          display: inline-block;
          padding: 3px 5px;
          font: 11px "SFMono-Regular", Consolas, "Liberation Mono", Menlo, monospace;
          line-height: 10px;
          color: #444d56;
          vertical-align: middle;
          background-color: #fafbfc;
          border: solid 1px #d1d5da;
          border-radius: 6px;
          box-shadow: inset 0 -1px 0 #d1d5da;
      }
  </style>
  <div class="p-6 space-y-4 text-sm">
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
      <li>Load audio, then set each word's start/end with the keys or the <strong>−/+</strong> buttons (50ms steps).</li>
      <li><strong>Split</strong> divides a word's time across the following words that have none.</li>
      <li><strong>Find issues</strong> lists problem ayahs across the surah — click one to jump to it.</li>
      <li><strong>Auto save</strong> saves automatically when you move to another ayah.</li>
      <li>Row colors: <span class="text-yellow-700">yellow = issue</span>, <span class="text-blue-700">blue = unsaved change</span>, <span class="text-green-700">green = current word</span>.</li>
    </ul>

    <div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Shortcuts</h3>
      <table class="w-full">
        <tbody>
        <% short_keys.each do |key, fun| %>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-0.5 pr-3 whitespace-nowrap"><kbd><%= key %></kbd></td>
            <td class="py-0.5"><%= fun %></td>
          </tr>
        <% end %>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
